ed="T" n="0758a09"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0758a09"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012499"><placeName>溫州</placeName><placeName>龍興寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010119">玄覺</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0758a10"/><persName key="A010119">釋玄覺</persName>，字<persName key="A010119">明道</persName>，俗姓<name>戴</name>氏，<date notBefore-iso="+0172-01-27" key="j17839081801742" notAfter-iso="+0220-11-25"><name>漢</name>末</date>祖<name>侃</name>公第五<lb
ed="T" n="0758a11"/><name>燕</name>公九代孫<ptr target="#n1347"/>，諱<persName key="A022587">烈</persName>，渡<placeName key="PL000000000150">江</placeName>，乃為<placeName key="PL000000012521">永嘉</placeName>人也。<anchor xml:id="beg0758001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>總</sic><corr>𩮀</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0758001"/><lb
ed="T" n="0758a12"/>角出家，齠年<ptr type="glossary" target="#g280"/>剃髮，心源本淨，智印<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1384"/>全文，測不<lb
ed="T" n="0758a13"/>可思，解甚深義。我與無我，恒常固知；空與<lb
ed="T" n="0758a14"/>不空，具足皆見。既離四病<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1385"/>，亦服三衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1386"/>。德水<lb
ed="T" n="0758a15"/>沐其身，所以清淨；良藥<ptr target="#n1348"/>治其眼，所以光明。<lb
ed="T" n="0758a16"/>兄<persName key="A010128">宣<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>者，亦名僧也。并猶子<ptr type="glossary" target="#g513"/>二人，並預緇<lb
ed="T" n="0758a17"/>伍<ptr target="#n1353"/>。<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>本住<placeName key="PL000000012499">龍興寺</placeName>，一門歸信，連影精勤，定<lb
ed="T" n="0758a18"/>根<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1388"/>確乎不移，疑樹<ptr target="#n1349"/>忽焉自壞。都捐我相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1389"/>，不<lb
ed="T" n="0758a19"/>污客塵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1390"/>。覩<ref type="place" target="#PL000000012499">其寺</ref>旁別有勝境，遂於巖下自<lb
ed="T" n="0758a20"/>構禪庵。滄海盪其胸，青山拱其背，<placeName key="PL000000055457">蓬萊</placeName>僊<lb
ed="T" n="0758a21"/>客，歲月往還；華蓋煙雲，晨昏交集。粵若功德<lb
ed="T" n="0758a22"/>成就，佛寶欝興；神鐘震來，妙屋化出。<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>居其<lb
ed="T" n="0758a23"/>間也，絲不以衣，耕不以食，豈伊<persName key="A002718">莊子</persName>大布<lb
ed="T" n="0758a24"/>為裳<ptr target="#n1350"/>，自有<persName key="A003861">阿難</persName>甘露作飯<ptr target="#n1358"/>。<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>以獨學孤陋，<lb
ed="T" n="0758a25"/>三人有師，與<placeName key="PL000000013615">東陽</placeName><persName key="A010129"><anchor xml:id="beg0758002"/>策<anchor xml:id="end0758002"/><roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n986"/>肩隨<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1391"/>，遊方詢道<ptr target="#n1242"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0758a26"/>謁<placeName key="PL000000030617">韶陽</placeName><persName key="A001719">能<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>而得旨焉<ptr target="#n1354"/>。或曰：「<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>振錫遶<lb
ed="T" n="0758a27"/>庵答對」，語在別錄<ptr target="#n1351"/>。至若<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>門庭，遐征問<lb
ed="T" n="0758a28"/>法，然終得心于<placeName key="PL000000030577">曹溪</placeName>耳。既決所疑，<persName key="A001719">能</persName>留一<lb
ed="T" n="0758a29"/>宿，號曰<persName key="A010119">一宿覺</persName>，猶<persName key="A001708">半遍清</persName>也<ptr target="#n1352"/>。以<date key="j19817941981794" when-iso="+0713-11-13"><name>先天</name>二年<pb ed="T" n="0758b" xml:id="T50.2061.0758b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0758b01"/>十月十七日</date>於<placeName key="PL000000012499">龍興</placeName>別院端坐入定，怡然不<lb
ed="T" n="0758b02"/>動。僧侶悲號，以<date key="j19818201981820" when-iso="+0713-12-09">其年十一月十三日</date>殯于<lb
ed="T" n="0758b03"/><placeName key="PL000000012493">西山</placeName>之陽，春秋四十九<ptr target="#n1355"/>。初<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>未亡前，禁足於<lb
ed="T" n="0758b04"/>西巖，望<ref type="place" target="#PL000000012499">所住寺</ref>喟然歎曰：「人物駢闐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1392"/>，花輿蓊<lb
ed="T" n="0758b05"/>蔚，何用之為！」其門人<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName><persName key="A010130">興<roleName>師</roleName></persName>、<placeName key="PL000000048606">新羅國</placeName><persName key="A010131">宣<roleName>師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0758b06"/>數人同聞，皆莫測之。尋而述之曰：「昔有一<lb
ed="T" n="0758b07"/>禪師，將諸弟子遊賞之次，遠望一山，忽而<lb
ed="T" n="0758b08"/>唱曰：『人物多矣。』弟子亦不測，後匪久此師<lb
ed="T" n="0758b09"/>捨壽，殯所望地也。」<placeName key="PL000000012493">西山</placeName>去寺里有餘程，送<lb
ed="T" n="0758b10"/>殯繁擁，人物沸騰，其感動也若此。又未終前，<lb
ed="T" n="0758b11"/>有舒雁<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1273"/>千餘飛于寺西，侍人曰：「此將何來？」<lb
ed="T" n="0758b12"/>空中有聲云：「為<ref type="person" target="#A010119">師</ref>墓所，故從海出也。」弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0758b13"/><persName key="A010132">惠操</persName>、<persName key="A010133">惠特</persName>、<persName key="A010134">等慈</persName>、<persName key="A010135">玄寂</persName>，皆傳<ref type="person" target="#A010119">師</ref>之法，為時所<lb
ed="T" n="0758b14"/>推。後<persName key="A007761">李<roleName>北海</roleName>邕</persName>為守<placeName key="PL000000014935">括州</placeName>，遂列<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>行錄為<lb
ed="T" n="0758b15"/>碑，號<persName key="A010119">神道</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0758sgsz1"/>焉<anchor xml:id="end0758sgsz1"/>。<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>唱道著明，修證悟入，<placeName key="PL000000045875">慶州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0758b16"/>刺史<persName key="A010136">魏靖</persName>都緝綴之，號《永嘉集》<ptr target="#n1356"/>是也。初<persName key="A010119">覺</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0758b17"/>與<placeName key="PL000000013557">左溪</placeName><persName key="A009605">朗<roleName>公</roleName></persName>為道契，<persName key="A009605">朗</persName>貽書招<persName key="A010119">覺</persName>山棲<ptr target="#n1238"/>。<persName key="A010119">覺</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0758b18"/>由是念<persName key="A009605">朗</persName>之滯見于山，拘情於講，迴書激<lb
ed="T" n="0758b19"/>勸<ptr target="#n1357"/>。其辭婉靡，其理明白。俾其山、世一如，喧、靜<lb
ed="T" n="0758b20"/>互用，趣入之意，暗詮于是，達者韙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1393"/>之。終，勅<lb
ed="T" n="0758b21"/>謚號<persName key="A010119">無相</persName>，塔曰<placeName key="PL000000056221">淨光</placeName>焉。</p>
